Linux Setup Instructions
------------------------

Install required services:

- PHP
- Database (mysql or postgres)
- PHP PDO:
-- sudo apt-get install php5-mysql 

Install PHP Depedencies:

- Install Composer if you don't have it:
- https://getcomposer.org/doc/00-intro.md
- Run the install command for composer. If you have a local composer installation this is:
-- php composer.phar install
- If you have a global install of composer you can do:
-- composer install

Setup DB:
- Copy db.ini.example to db.ini
- Edit database connection for your database
- Import database structure, e.g. mysql -u user -p < db.sql

